To improve the performance of recipes run after a full local Salesforce object sync, choose to optimize the synced data.

Available in: Salesforce Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited Editions, Developer Edition.
Use this feature at your own risk. It is not generally available and may be discontinued with no notice. 

Go to Data Manager, Connections tab, SFDC_LOCAL object, Data Sync Settings tab, select Optimize data sync for future runs.

Recommended: test in a sandbox environment.
title: Optimizing Local Salesforce Connection in CRM Analytics
